# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if the platform is not identical, the lock file should be omitted.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock contains dependency versions.
